genresAdvancedInfo.name: dutch underground hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Dutch underground hip hop is a subgenre of hip hop that originated in the Netherlands. It is characterized by its raw and gritty sound, often featuring socially conscious lyrics and political themes. This genre is known for its DIY approach, with many artists producing and distributing their music independently.
